snippet.title: The MacMaster
snippet.description:
Hi I'm Lee, otherwise known as  The MacMaster. I'm from Nottingham in England. I make vlogs about TRAVEL, FOOD and TECH. I'm a Graphic Designer and Film Maker. I use Apple Mac, shoot my movies with Lumix GH5, Sony A7 III, iPhone 13 Mini, iPhone 13 Pro, iPhone 13 Pro Max, Insta 360 Go2, DJI Phantom 4, DJI Mavic Mini and edit my movies with Final Cut Pro. I upload daily, if you like my vlogs, give them the thumbs up, subscribe and hit the bell for notifications of when I upload new content. 

Welcome to the family and enjoy the ride.
